@startuml
title Arquitectura Física y Stack Tecnológico — Jorgestor

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam node {
  BackgroundColor #f8fafc
  BorderColor #64748b
}

node "Máquina del Usuario" as ClientNode {
  component "Navegador Web" as Browser
  package "Frontend (puerto 5173)" {
    component "React 18 + Vite" as React
    component "TypeScript" as TS
    component "TanStack Query v5" as TQ
    component "React Router v6" as RR
    component "Axios" as Axios
  }
}

node "Servidor de Aplicaciones" as ServerNode {
  package "Spring Boot 3.2.5 (JVM 21 — puerto 9090)" {
    component "Controladores REST\n(@RestController)" as Controllers
    component "Servicios de Negocio\n(@Service)" as Services
    component "Repositorios\n(Spring Data JPA)" as Repos

    note right of Services
      - Algoritmo generarYAsignar
      - Motor de calificación
        (aciertos - fallos/3) / total × 10
      - Hashing SHA-256 (claveCorreccion)
      - RBAC (Docente / Admin)
    end note
  }
}

node "Servidor de Datos" as DBNode {
  database "PostgreSQL 17" as DB
  note right of DB
    Tablas principales:
    examenes, examen_alumnos,
    marcas_examen_alumno,
    preguntas, respuestas,
    alumnos, profesores, usuarios,
    asignaturas, grados, temas,
    matriculas (N:M),
    examen_preguntas (N:M),
    asignatura_grados (N:M)
  end note
}

' ─── Flujo de comunicación ───────────────────────────────────────
Browser    --> React       : renderiza
React      --> Axios       : llamadas HTTP
Axios      -down-> Controllers : REST / JSON (CORS habilitado)
Controllers -down-> Services  : inyección de dependencias
Services   -down-> Repos      : consultas JPA
Repos      -down-> DB         : SQL / JDBC (HikariCP)

center footer © 2026 Jorgestor — Ingeniería del Software II (IDSW2)
@enduml
